  "description": "Refrigeration fundamentals, cryogenic air separation, and gas liquefaction and storage. Covers vapor-compression through Claude cycle refrigeration, double-column distillation at -196°C, expansion turbine engineering, dewar vessel design, and cryogenic insulation systems. Produces liquid and gaseous N₂, O₂, and Ar at industrial scale for semiconductor fabrication.",
